title: precise definition -- at least of a special case
pid: dfa3372a-3dea-4c26-8a12-31ffba86ab3c
body: |2-
  when a tree has
    a node S (for source)
      that has (maybe among other links)
      a link L to node T (for target)
        (T maybe needing to be part of a different tree),
  and S contains S'
  and T contains T'
    such that S' links to T'
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
